<h1>Ably Connection Example</h1>

<p>In this example, we demonstrate the the simplest way to attach a channel and subscribe to channel state events. See <a href="https://www.ably.io/documentation/realtime/channel">our Realtime Connection documentation</a> for more details.

<div class="row">
  <input id="attach" type="submit" value="Attach channel">
  <input id="detach" type="submit" value="Detach channel">
</div>

<div class="row" id="channel-status"></div>
